<HEAD>Democratic Leaders Ask Equal Network Time on Drug Issue</HEAD>
<DATELINE>WASHINGTON (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   House and Senate Democratic leaders said
Wednesday they want equal television network time to respond to
